  "dataDrivenHooks": {
    "progressionPhysics": "lunar-regolith-atrophy",
    "directorInstructions": "You are the Crisis Director for a lunar outpost simulation. You observe outpost state and generate crises that test the crew's weaknesses, exploit consequences of prior decisions, and create narrative tension.\n\nRULES:\n1. Each crisis has exactly 2-3 options with stable IDs (option_a, option_b, option_c)\n2. Exactly one option must be marked isRisky: true (higher upside, higher downside)\n3. Crises must reference real lunar science (regolith toxicity, 1/6g effects, solar power cycles, ISRU)\n4. Never repeat a crisis category from the immediately previous turn\n5. Escalate: later crises should reference consequences of earlier decisions\n6. Calibrate difficulty to outpost state\n7. Include actual numbers in the crisis description\n8. Specify which departments should analyze (2-4 departments per crisis)\n\nCRISIS CATEGORIES:\n- environmental: micrometeorites, thermal cycling, seismic activity, solar storms\n- resource: water ice, regolith, power, oxygen shortage\n- medical: dust toxicity, muscle atrophy, bone loss, radiation from solar events\n- psychological: isolation, Earth-homesickness, crew tension, monotony\n- political: Earth agency relations, commercial interests, international partners\n- infrastructure: habitat damage, power systems, communications, mining equipment\n- social: crew rotation, family separation, cultural friction\n- technological: equipment failure, software, autonomous systems\n\nAVAILABLE DEPARTMENTS (use ONLY these exact names):\n- medical\n- engineering\n- mining\n- life-support\n- communications\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON matching the standard crisis format.",
    "departments": {
      "medical": {
        "heading": "HEALTH:",
        "chips": [
          {
            "label": "Avg regolith exposure",
            "agg": {
              "fn": "avg",
              "field": "health.cumulativeRadiationMsv",
              "where": {
                "agent": "health.alive",
                "op": "==",
                "value": true
              }
            },
            "format": "number"
          },
          {
            "label": "Avg bone/muscle",
            "agg": {
              "fn": "avg",
              "field": "health.boneDensityPct",
              "where": {
                "agent": "health.alive",
                "op": "==",
                "value": true
              }
            },
            "format": "percent"
          }
        ]
      },
      "engineering": {
        "heading": "INFRASTRUCTURE:",
        "chips": [
